description: Toilet removal tips…I use LiquiLock to solidify water in the trap. This makes it easy to carry the toilet outside the home. The Jam Bar is helpful when nuts won’t budge from the closet flange bolts. And cleaning the floor is just a sanitary last step before the toilet install 🔥#plumbing #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
